content: Xander's new feature for personal eco-tips got positive feedback at our last pop-up. Emily and I are now focusing on how to make him even more proactive in real-time decision-making for ethical trading.

Finalized the ethical trading module for the DeFi conference - it's our biggest showcase yet. Emily's AI art exhibition is set to open next week, and Xander will be there to interact with guests. Exciting times!
